{"tid":1030404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合醫院送發霉柑打氣 前線員工斥最毒祝福","createTime":"2019-02-21T02:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T02:35:51.000Z","uid":56881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16b5a828d3426bec6ba783014c6eb6db39bba360","tid":1030404,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:35:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%81%E7%99%BC%E9%9C%89%E6%9F%91%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3-%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%AF%92%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F-214500987.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2580%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%259C%2589%25E6%259F%2591%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%25AF%2592%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%25A6%258F-214500987.html&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=ddcb0537\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%81%E7%99%BC%E9%9C%89%E6%9F%91%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3-%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%96%A5%E6%9C%80%E6%AF%92%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F-214500987.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2I3diMC8kZpvJfT_oZaaVg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/c9133b03172456fd3bc79c9043c9eef6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2I3diMC8kZpvJfT_oZaaVg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fc9133b03172456fd3bc79c9043c9eef6&h=05590ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】流感高峰期未過，公立醫院前線醫護人員忙個不停。聯合醫院前日向前線同事送柑打氣及安撫員工士氣，卻演變成公關災難，員工發現該批柑不少已經發霉，院方卻懵然不知照送可也，質疑是否真的關心同事。有前線護士形容，院方送上的是「最毒的祝福」，「即係我要做到好『甘』」並批評院方不夠誠意，進一步打擊前線士氣，「送柑真係好&times;毒」。<br />\n<br />\n新春送柑被指意頭差<br />\n<br />\n基督教聯合醫務協會趁着新春伊始，日前將一箱箱甜柑送到聯合醫院，準備派送給各病房的前線醫護同事，原意是對員工表達謝意，並祝他們身體健康，生活愉快。但據了解，各病房醫護人員接收該批生果後，紛紛表現不悅，一來送柑意頭不好，而且更發現當中大批柑已經發霉，根本不能食用，「上次送過一次，嗰個星期已經好&times;柑，今次仲要送霉！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SkAwytsvy9_mlrAp6hWg6g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/0d41ffb6696bd173a0e3036391014939\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSkAwytsvy9_mlrAp6hWg6g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F0d41ffb6696bd173a0e3036391014939&h=7d3b2d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n班高層真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}